Comment: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.99,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The famous high school detective Shin'ichi Kudo
Comment: 0,0:00:03.99,0:00:05.66,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}was forced to take a strange poison by a certain organization,
Comment: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.36,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}causing him to shrink and become Conan Edogawa!
Comment: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:09.57,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Doesn't matter if I'm small!
Comment: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.50,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My mind's that of a brilliant 17-year old detective!
Comment: 0,0:00:11.50,0:00:14.40,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll solve another case today that would have adults shaking in their boots!
Comment: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I, Genta Kojima, will be club leader!
Comment: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Any objections?!
Comment: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope!
Comment: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:24.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6\c&H4FAF&\fscx100\fs48}BAM! SMASH! CRASH!
Comment: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:03.00,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! There's still something I want to ask you!
Comment: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:05.62,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who has the bomb?!
Comment: 0,0:24:05.62,0:24:08.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is it? I can't find—
Comment: 0,0:24:15.16,0:24:17.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's only one way to make her believe me!
Comment: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:20.62,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I tell her that I'm actually Shin'ichi Kudo!
Comment: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:23.92,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you really?
Comment: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:45.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6}Next Conan:
Comment: 0,0:24:45.43,0:24:50.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Cell Phone
Comment: 0,0:24:39.36,0:24:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Next time's gonna keep you on the edge of your seat. Be sure to watch!
Comment: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:06.32,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
