Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:29.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6}"Secret Treasures of the World Exhibit"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:33.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Totally awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A map to buried treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:40.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That sure was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I really liked that gold mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:45.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There's still tons of secret treasure all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:48.07,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,that hasn't been discovered yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:51.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,For reals?! I wanna try and find some!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with this piece of paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It has a bunch of strange symbols on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Maybe it's a treasure map!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Are you sayin' you can't believe what Ayumi says?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you getting so mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:21.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:24.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Ayumi's definitely right about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:29.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What if it really is a 100% genuine treasure map?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly! What if it is a real map?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.22,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright then! Let's go treasure hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:44.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,From this day forth we'll be known as the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Detective Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That sounds so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.24,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}My head's starting to hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:52.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:58.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Let me have a look at that piece of paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at this very top symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Haven't you seen this somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:19.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:30.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Dino Cavane, the Italian crime lord who was arrested last night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:36.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,at an apartment complex near Tohto Tower, has so far refused to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:40.66,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The police are currently pursuing Cavane's accomplices,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.66,0:04:42.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but they have been unable to find any clues leading to their whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:46.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The location of the 15,000 Maple Leaf gold coins they stole
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,is also unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:49.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,"To Tohto Tower"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:56.31,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought the Tohto Tower was suspicious from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now the treasure is as good as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But what do you think these letters mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It says "ORO" here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.39,Signs,Comment,0,0,0,,orochi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,G-Giant serpent?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet it's an abbreviation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.69,Signs,Comment,0,0,0,,ōkii
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The first O stands for "big"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:15.53,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The R means rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.13,Signs,Comment,0,0,0,,o-takara
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:18.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And the last O stands for "treasure"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:23.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So that means it's a big treasure that will make you rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:27.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow! I didn't know you could read English, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet it's a huge treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:40.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright! I'm gonna use that treasure to eat the world's best eel dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go around the world 100 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:47.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy a space shuttle from NASA and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.63,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What about you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll save it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You don't know how to have fun, do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:54.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:07.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright! Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,All that's left is to decipher the code!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But none of the other symbols look like anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:15.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,except for the one that looks like an umbrella...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:22.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! It's the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:27.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The treasure must be where the moon and Tohto Tower line up like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:30.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The moon's position{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ges everyday,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:36.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and I doubt you could specify exact locations with such simple drawings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Then where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:42.01,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, did you figure anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:47.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I was wondering if the other symbols are abbreviations for things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:50.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Like this symbol beneath the tower could be a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:52.83,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Beneath that might be underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:56.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The umbrella beneath that could be an emblem on a sweater or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:59.57,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And the thing that links them all together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A clothes store!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But this isn't enough to really—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.41,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:05.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6}"Terahara Clothing Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:22.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There has to be a clue in here somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:25.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it, you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid little kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I never want to see you here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Looks like it didn't have to do with clothing stores after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:41.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I sure am hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna go eat something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.65,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we stop by a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:51.22,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! You can't eat anything at a bookstore!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just for a short while. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:55.99,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.21,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, check this out! It's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.43,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:06.04,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6}"English-to-Japanese Dictionary"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.10,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}O. R. O. ORO?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.72,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was there such a word in English?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.57,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}No luck, it's not in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.56,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.78,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Italian...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:21.04,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I really doubt it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.85,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.79,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oro in Italian means gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:33.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means this code really does show where treasure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:41.70,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6}"Mouri Detective Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.16,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The accomplices of the Italian crime lord Dino Cavane,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:41.64,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}who was caught yesterday, are currently in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.27,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The whereabouts of the 15,000 Maple Leaf coins they stole
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.51,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}are, as of yet, unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:51.24,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}These coins, which total over 600 million in Japanese yen, were—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:54.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,600 million, huh? These guys must know what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:58.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You've trashed the place up again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.58,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you get any worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That reminds me, where's the runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If you mean Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, he left early this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,to go to the art museum with his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:15.67,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Kids sure got it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:20.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad! At least help clean up a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.01,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.28,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}According to Italian authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:32.12,Radio,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}three of Cavane's accomplices are on the run, and one of them is Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up with Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.86,0:09:45.50,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How should I know? That's all he's been doing since we got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you think maybe he figured something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.00,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's hopeless! I can't figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:53.14,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this code?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:57.10,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it a map? Or is it some kind of message?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:05.62,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Could that be it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,See! That sign! It looks just like the second symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:13.06,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:15.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Could these symbols actually represent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:21.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It has to be! This shop's directly in front of Tohto Tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:25.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and the next symbol has the shape of this sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:30.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So if we follow this order of store signs we'll find the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:33.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But which way should we go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.59,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Moon View Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.75,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Could the moon symbol next to the tower actually represent Moon View Street?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:49.16,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet it does! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Look! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.04,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,An upside-down triangle sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:59.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right! It looks just like the third symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:03.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So these symbols really do represent—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.61,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,An aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:11.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This code is a map from Tohto Tower to the Nanbu Aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:16.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,They drew the signs and displays of stores along Moon View Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:19.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And the final destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...is a mountain of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:40.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't see the fifth star-shaped symbol anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:44.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! And we were so close to the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.15,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:48.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We've made it all the way to the aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:50.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.73,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.26,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}We never even found the fifth symbol on Moon View Street
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:59.37,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}between Tohto Tower and the Nanbu Aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.77,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or am I assuming something incorrectly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:06.24,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait. Why is "gold" written in Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:09.64,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the person who wrote this was Italian, then the moon symbol...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.38,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:17.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We need to go back to where we started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.77,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's hard to think that the person who wrote "gold" in Italian
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.21,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}would use the moon symbol to represent Moon View Street—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.31,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}which is in Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:42.64,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The moon represents night—and the things you can only see at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.88,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Neon signs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan! What did you figure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:53.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a treasure map comprised of the shapes of various neon signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:57.08,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The neon sign in the second symbol is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.27,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:05.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:08.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Next we go down by the stadium!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:11.24,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We just need to find an umbrella-shaped sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:14.98,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't see any umbrella-shaped signs anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you've got it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I already found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.95,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,{\a6}"Tomorrow's Weather"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:26.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? That's the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! The symbol for rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:33.09,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Rain must've been in the forecast for the day after they wrote the code!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Next is a neon sign shaped like a star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.81,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A Ferris Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.91,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it! It's the fifth symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:49.38,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So we should see the sixth sign from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:52.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,There it is! The sixth neon sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.77,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Conan, there's really gonna be treasure here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:20.71,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. This symbol has "ORO" written next to it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:24.85,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been looking for the last fish-shaped sign for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:28.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,but I just can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a residential street. There's nothing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The closest fish would probably be in a nearby river or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's it! The river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.73,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It must mean a river with fish in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:40.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.10,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's go check out the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:49.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's dangerous, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:56.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit yer yappin'! The treasure has to be at the bottom of this river!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.72,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:04.02,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! This code represents things you can only see at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:08.52,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}So the fish symbol at the end can't represent the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:13.13,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my guess is correct, then it has to be somewhere nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.70,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}A fish-shaped neon light...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.51,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:37.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The glowing fish, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.42,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A glowing fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:45.32,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Never heard of any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:47.94,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.47,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come on already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there really gonna be a glowing fish here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:59.18,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! It's so dark I can't see anything, much less any fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Take a look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:03.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Towards that river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:04.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The river?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.52,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,See! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:08.89,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the glowing fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.76,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The lights are reflected on the water and make it look like a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.00,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And the fish's eye is the light on the building in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Does that mean the treasure's in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:23.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's probably located right around...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,...here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A gold coin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.66,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's that black shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:47.23,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It looks like it's connected to a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.56,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:50.46,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}They raised the sacks of gold coins up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:53.06,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}by looping the rope around part of the ceiling that sticks out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:02.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.45,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help, kiddos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.39,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:16.32,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Weren't they the ones I saw in front of Tohto Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.29,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait! Maybe they're the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:22.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it back! We found those first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:28.40,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:34.01,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see. They still don't know where the coins are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:36.84,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Members of that Italian crime ring, most likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Crime ring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:45.02,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I heard about them on the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That means those coins just now must've been—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.82,0:17:50.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:55.46,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We swiped these coins from an Italian bank a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:58.13,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Just like our boss Cavane told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:18:02.44,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But then he backstabbed us and ran off to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:06.93,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,With the 15,000 Maple Leaf coins in tow, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.90,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We tailed him to Japan and paid him a visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.55,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But he had hidden the coins somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:19.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell us where he hid 'em, no matter how much we interrogated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:23.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,All we found at his place was this code!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:26.86,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He wouldn't help us out, so we informed the police of his location,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:31.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and set out in search of the coins ourselves, relying only on his code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:36.29,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The wind blew the paper away when we stopped by the art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,But we saw you cracking the code little by little,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:42.37,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,so we decided to let you keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:46.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Never imagined you'd actually find it for us though!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:50.68,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,A gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:19:00.30,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,So tell me! Where are the coins?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.23,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You better speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.17,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.14,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.97,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,The coins are hidden at the location where the fish symbol
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:14.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,and the night view of the bridge outside match up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:24.05,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan! What'd you tell him for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:27.69,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We're as good as dead once they find the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:30.86,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're gonna kill us no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:35.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,They're gonna shoot us to death, I bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:40.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I bet they're gonna stick us in cement and drop us into the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, they're going to burn us to death so there's no proof left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:48.34,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.04,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too early to give up just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:58.12,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We still have a{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.82,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,If we all work together, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.49,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,How will that do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:05.96,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We're just children!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:08.62,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't we the Detective Boys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Alright! So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Get up. But make sure they don't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.27,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}We only have one shot at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:33.55,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}The moment that they find the coins and let their guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.69,Thoughts,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.28,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:09.79,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:14.40,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}Afterward, we went straight to a nearby police station
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:16.93,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}and explained everything that had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:21.17,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}To everyone's delight, the gang was arrested and the case was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:24.97,Narration Off,Comment,0,0,0,,{\be10}It wound up being the Detective Boys' very first accomplishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:58.56,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,You're amazing! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:01.03,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe you cracked that code!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:02.74,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And you even captured some thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:05.20,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It was me! I caught them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.77,0:23:08.33,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,And I used my reasoning to decipher the code!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:12.48,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't listen to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:18.54,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,It was Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} who cracked the code and beat up the gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.62,0:23:23.25,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,He was so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:30.60,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:32.36,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.54,0:23:41.64,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Good for you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! You've made a cute little girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:44.11,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:46.35,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Now he's embarrassed! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:48.87,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,No, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:52.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Lousy Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.79,0:23:55.88,Dialogue,Comment,0,0,0,,Lousy Conan!
